    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>MASTERS OF MARTIAL ARTS</strong><br />Members of the Gouken clan, consistently throughout the ages, are born with exceptional talent in Martial Arts, even though they are spread throughout the world. Whether they are teachers or students of the Arts or just fighters on the streets, the power of Ki the Gouken possess and their indomitable will always make them a formidable opponent to face.</p><p><strong>GOUKEN TRAITS</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Constitution or Strength, +1 to Strength or Intelligence (You cannot choose Strength twice for the ASIs).</p></li><li><p><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 30 feet.</p></li><li><p><strong>Proficiencies:</strong> You gain Proficiency in Martial Arts and Ninshou, as well as one artisan tool of your choice.</p></li><li><p><strong>Passive Affinity:</strong> You gain the Fire Release Nature Release.</p></li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
